<div class="bg-white py-24 sm:py-32">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
      <p class="text-base/7 font-semibold text-sky-500">Commerce</p>
      <h1 class="mt-2 text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-6xl">
        Commerce built for modern service businesses
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg font-medium text-gray-600 sm:text-xl/8">
        Accept payments, manage services, and power your operations with a secure, flexible commerce engine built into Business OS — designed for clinics, barbershops, studios, and commercial teams.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="bg-white pb-24 sm:pb-32">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 text-base/7 text-gray-600">

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Sell with confidence</h2>
        <p class="mt-4">
          Our commerce engine gives you everything you need to sell services, products, memberships, and subscriptions. From secure payments to service-based workflows, we provide the tools that help you grow without complexity.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-6">
          Whether you're accepting deposits for appointments or managing recurring billing, our platform adapts to your business model.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Built for performance</h2>
        <p class="mt-4">
          Fast, reliable, and optimized for conversions. Our commerce tools deliver a seamless experience for your customers — from booking to checkout.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-6">
          With built-in analytics, automation, and bilingual support (EN/ES), you can focus on growth while Business OS handles the infrastructure.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="bg-gray-50 py-24 sm:py-32">
